# Dev commands (chat / slash)

Prefer these npm scripts when the user asks to start servers or run checks:

| Task | Slash command | npm script |
|------|---------------|------------|
| Mobile + iOS sim | `/mobile-dev` | `npm run mobile:dev` |
| Mobile Metro only | `/mobile-metro` | `npm run mobile:start` |
| Web Next.js | `/web-dev` | `npm run dev` |
| Xcode diagnose | `/xcode-check` | `npm run xcode:check` |
| Unit tests | `/test` | `npm run test` |
| Type-check | `/type-check` | see `/type-check` command |

Slash commands live in `.cursor/commands/*.md`. Type `/` in chat to pick one.

Long-running servers: run in background with network permissions. Never run `sudo` unless the user explicitly requests it in chat.
